<% content_for :learn do %>
  <ul>
    <li>
      How to refactor JavaScript into clean code
    </li>
    <li>
      The 10 conventions that speed up reading and writing JavaScript for Rails
    </li>
    <li>
      How to organise JavaScript files (and why Webpacker is good fun)
    </li>
